00:40:29.550 --> 00:40:30.809
(GROWLING)

931
00:40:30.889 --> 00:40:33.139
Machiavelli! (SHUSHES) Don't you...
Machiavelli! Đừng có mà...

932
00:40:33.230 --> 00:40:35.639
- No! Machiavelli! - (LUCA SCREAMING)
Không! Machiavelli!

933
00:40:36.900 --> 00:40:37.980
(LUCA PANTING)

934
00:40:38.059 --> 00:40:39.769
I'm so sorry about the cat.
Tớ rất xin lỗi về con mèo.

935
00:40:39.860 --> 00:40:41.360
I don't know what got into him.
Tớ không biết nó bị cái gì nữa.

936
00:40:41.440 --> 00:40:44.320
It's fine. We're gonna head back to, uh...
