1019
00:43:52.760 --> 00:43:53.969
- (GRUNTS) - (MACHIAVELLI YOWLS)

1020
00:43:54.050 --> 00:43:55.679
- (WATER SPLASHES) - (LUCA GASPS AND WHIMPERS)

1021
00:43:56.300 --> 00:43:57.889
(GROWLING)

1022
00:44:02.889 --> 00:44:04.019
(GRUNTS SOFTLY)

1023
00:44:14.860 --> 00:44:16.489
A sea monster ate it.
Một con quái vật đại dương đã ăn nó rồi.

1024
00:44:16.860 --> 00:44:17.989
Huh? What?
Hả? Gì?

1025
00:44:18.489 --> 00:44:22.500
(CHUCKLES) Ma, no. This is how I came into the world.
Ma, no. Đây là cách chú đến với thế giới này.

1026
00:44:24.500 --> 00:44:25.710
(GRUNTING)

1027
00:44:27.880 --> 00:44:28.880
Whoa.

1028
00:44:28.960 --> 00:44:31.630
Mannaggia, not a great catch today.
