Đến lúc ta phải về nhà rồi.

1052
00:45:34.860 --> 00:45:35.860
(KID YELPS)

1053
00:45:38.780 --> 00:45:39.820
(PANTS)

1054
00:45:41.070 --> 00:45:42.329
(WHIMPERS)

1055
00:45:42.409 --> 00:45:43.989
(SOBBING LOUDLY)

1056
00:45:44.079 --> 00:45:46.369
(FUMBLES FOR WORDS) Let that be a lesson to you!
Hãy xem đó là bài học cho em!

1057
00:45:46.460 --> 00:45:48.619
Go, go, go! Run before its mother gets here!
Đi, đi! Chạy lẹ kẻo mẹ nó tới!

1058
00:45:49.579 --> 00:45:51.170
It turns out I don't got this.
Hoá ra anh chả hiểu gì.

1059
00:45:51.250 --> 00:45:54.340
